node.text: We want to give a HUGE Welcome back to Co-Owner Lauren from her maternity leave!! 👶🏻 To all the working  Mommas out there we sure know how it feels to come back to work after being home with your baby for awhile and all of the challenges it brings:) We also wanted to give the BIGGEST shout out to Kelly, Bill and Molly and the rest of our Beachwood staff for keeping things running so smoothly at our Laplace  location and to Maureen and our Solon staff for holding things down during one of our BIGGEST growth periods as a company we’ve ever experienced. 😱We are just grateful all around for each and every one of you that supports our company including our Amazing customers. 💕 Both shops open today for walk in-Beachwood 11-6, Solon Noon-6 and we are fully stocked with so many sweets for you weekend🎉 Photo by @balsam_bill_hikes #whiteflowercakeshoppe #buttercream #cakesofinstagram #buttercreamflowers #Cleveland

node.text: What do you guys think, Too early for fall colors??? We can’t help ourselves thinking about all of the delicious fall menu items we have planned for you next month. Stay tuned for details!!! Both shops open for walk in today, Beachwood 11-6 Solon 12-6 we can’t wait to see your smiling faces!💕 #whiteflowercakeshoppe #instacake #buttercream #buttercreamlove #cake #cleveland

node.text: Beachwood is hiring! Have you always wanted a behind the scenes look at how White Flower makes it all happen? Wanted a first taste of new flavors before they hit the case? Dreamed of a supportive and tight-knit group of co-workers that become lifelong friends? Then look no further! We’d love to add you to our team! See the second slide for more details and learn how to apply. We will be reaching out quickly to schedule interviews. We can’t wait to meet you!
